    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i don't have any tylenol or advil here, i only have the aspirin. is it really that dangerous? i feel like most medicine is basically the same thing for fevers. if i just give him like half a tablet, surely that won't cause a whole syndrome or anything? i really need to get this fever down so he can sleep.",
